featured_reviews.review_id:
Also known as Safed Masjid or Qazi ki Masjid by the Locals.
It's a beautiful Nawab era mosque of Erstwhile state of Dujana with beautiful calligraphy both inside and outside of it.
Unfortunately due to a natural calamity and poor maintenance much of the masjid is lost today.
Still people could visit and have an idea about its beauty in its heydays.
